INSERT INTO news VALUES(1154,'https://blog.ethereum.org/en/2026/02/24/staking','Treasury Staking Initiative','The Ethereum Foundation has begun staking a portion of its treasury, in line with its Treasury Policy announced last year.  Approximately 70,000 ETH is being staked with rewards directed back to the EF treasury....','https://via.placeholder.com/400x250?text=Tech+News','2026-02-24T00:00:00','Ethereum Foundation','Web3');
INSERT INTO news VALUES(1155,'https://blog.ethereum.org/en/2026/02/23/commitment-to-defi','The Ethereum Foundation''s Commitment to DeFi','DeFi isn''t a speculative bet on the future. It''s the inevitable evolution of finance, driven by a fundamental truth: financial autonomy is a right, not a privilege. And it''s been a critical driver of Ethereum''s growth and adoption.  We want to see De','https://via.placeholder.com/400x250?text=Tech+News','2026-02-23T00:00:00','Ethereum Foundation','Web3');
INSERT INTO news VALUES(1156,'https://blog.ethereum.org/en/2026/02/18/protocol-priorities-update-2026','Protocol Priorities Update for 2026','We introduced Protocol last June which organized our work around three strategic initiatives: Scale L1, Scale Blobs, and Improve UX. A lot has happened since then! In this post, we want to share what we accomplished last year, how our thinking has ev','https://via.placeholder.com/400x250?text=Tech+News','2026-02-18T00:00:00','Ethereum Foundation','Web3');
